data.title: Tech Sector Leads as Stocks Move Higher
data.text: With tech stocks leading the market higher, Apple is separating from the pack, but Intel is not nimble enough to keep up.

data.title: The Strongest Components Of The Dow Jones Industrial Average — And The Weakest
data.text: With the run-up in price from the late December, 2018 lows, some Dow components have rallied to higher prices than last year’s peaks and some are having trouble keeping up.

data.title: 4 Blue-Chip Stocks Rallying in 2019 Amid Slowdown Concern
data.text: Some blue-chip stocks have however surged, defying all odds, and still have upside left for the rest of this year.
